<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Subscription Renewal Reminder</title>
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 20px;
          border: 1px solid #ddd;
          border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .header {
          text-align: center;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
          margin: 0;
      }
      .content {
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #777;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Subscription Renewal Reminder</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>,</p>
    <p>We hope you are enjoying our services at SmartEDU. This is a friendly reminder that your subscription is set to expire on <%= @school.subscription_end.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.</p>
    <p>To continue enjoying uninterrupted access to our services, please renew your subscription before the expiration date.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:smarteduccc@gmail.com">smarteduccc@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a valued member of SmartEDU!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> SmartEDU. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
